Package: tptest
Type: Package
Title: Universal Turning Point and Inflection Point Test
Version: 1.0.4
Date: 2026-03-20
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Tests for U-shaped and inverse U-shaped (hump-shaped) nonlinear
    relationships in regression models. Extends Lind and Mehlum (2010)
    <doi:10.1111/j.1468-0084.2009.00569.x> to quadratic, cubic,
    log-quadratic, and inverse functional forms. Implements the Sasabuchi
    (1980) joint slope test, delta-method standard errors for the turning
    point, Fieller confidence intervals, and the Simonsohn (2018) two-lines
    robustness test. Works as a post-estimation command after any model that
    returns a coefficient vector and variance-covariance matrix.
